et/pictures/content/writerdirector-david-mich%C3%B4d|accessdate=19 April 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110043235/http://www.m2e.net/pictures/content/writerdirector-david-mich%C3%B4d|archivedate=10 November 2014|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://www.squarethemovie.com/}}\n* {{Amg movie|463272|The Square}}\n* {{IMDb title|id=1085507|title=The Square}}\n*{{Metacritic film|the-square|The Square}}\n*{{Rotten Tomatoes|square|The Square}}\n*{{Mojo title|square10|The Square}}\n\n{{Joel Edgerton}}\n{{Nash Edgerton}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Square, The}}\n[[Category:2008 films]]\n[[Category:Australian films]]\n[[Category:English-language films]]\n[[Category:Directorial debut films]]\n[[Category:2000s crime thriller films]]\n[[Category:Australian neo-noir films]]\n[[Category:Australian thriller films]]\n[[Category:Films with screenplays by Joel Edgerton]]\n", "name_user": "Rich Farmbrough", "label": "safe", "comment": "Update date format tag", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Square_(2008_film)"}
